<paragraph blockId="35.[189,1399,382,549]" pageId="35" pageNumber="123">
<keyLead pageId="35" pageNumber="123">
− Species with mostly dark face, frons, lateral sides of scutum and most of terga; oral margin protruded (
<figureCitation box="[243,367,523,549]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="16.[189,232,1846,1872]" captionTargetBox="[424,1221,275,1807]" captionTargetId="figure-12@16.[366,1221,265,1807]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="Fig. 9. Male head, lateral view. A. Merodon bombiformis Hull, 1944 (FSUNS; FSUNS ZA2_079). B. M. multifasciatus Curran, 1939 (USNM 2052372; FSUNS ID 04512). C. M. vittatus Vujić &amp; Likov sp. nov., holotype (NBCN; FSUNS ID 04085). D. M. zebra Vujić &amp; Radenković sp. nov., holotype (RMCA; FSUNS ID 25089). E. M. lotus Vujić &amp; Radenković sp. nov., paratype (FSUNS; FSUNS ID ZA6_066). F. M. nasicus Bezzi, 1915 (TAUI; FSUNS ID 04972). Scale bar = 2 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5013026" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5013026/files/figure.png" pageId="35" pageNumber="123">Fig. 9B–F</figureCitation>
); antennal segments longer (
<figureCitation box="[703,824,523,549]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="8.[189,232,1848,1874]" captionTargetBox="[231,1357,265,1811]" captionTargetId="figure-11@8.[231,1357,265,1811]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="Fig. 4. Male antenna, lateral view. A. Merodon bombiformis Hull, 1944 (FSUNS; FSUNS ID ZA2_079). B. M. multifasciatus Curran, 1939 (USNM; FSUNS ID 04512). C. M. vittatus Vujić &amp; Likov sp. nov., holotype (NBCN; FSUNS ID 04085). D. M. zebra Vujić &amp; Radenković sp. nov. paratype (NBCN; FSUNS ID 05174). E. M. lotus Vujić &amp; Radenković sp. nov., paratype (FSUNS; FSUNS ID ZA6_066). F. M. nasicus Bezzi, 1915 (TAUI; FSUNS ID 04972). Scale bar = 2 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5013014" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5013014/files/figure.png" pageId="35" pageNumber="123">Fig. 4B–F</figureCitation>
) ......................................................................... 2
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
